# User stories and security 

###### All users
| # | As ... | I want ... | So I ... | Security | MoSCoW | Status |
| ------ | ------ | ------ | ------ | ------ | ------ | ------ |
| U0001 | User | to listen to music | I can listen to the music | None | Must have | TODO |
| U0002 | User | to learn new things | get a better knowlegde | None | Must have | TODO |
| U0003 | User | to search for a specific word | find more info about that word | SQL injection | Must have | TODO |
| U0004 | User | to have controls for the audio player | can pauze the songs, change volume, etc | None | Must have | TODO |
| U0005 | User | to fill in a contact form | can contact the website owner | Protect against SQL-injection & other forms of penetration, valid email | Must have | TODO |
| U0006 | User | to read more info when i am interested | can learn more | None | Could have | TODO |
| U0007 | User | a navigation menu | can navigate the website | None | Must have | TODO |
| U0008 | User | an agenda | can look at dates | SQL injection | Could have | TODO |


##### Admins
| # | As ... | I want ... | So I ... | Security | MoSCoW | Status |
| ------ | ------ | ------ | ------ | ------ | ------ | ------ |
| B0001 | Admin | to upload more info | get more content on my website |  SQL-injection | Must have | TODO |
| B0002 | Admin | to add new dates | can share concert dates | SQL-injection | Must have | TODO |
| B0003 | Admin | to update my content | can update the website's information | SQL-injection & XSS | Must have | TODO |
| B0004 | Admin | to add more search keywords | can give users more search options | SQL-injection & XSS | Must have | TODO |


